         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288"><!-- p3l6-r9 -->
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Hd1e108">Rubrica 9</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De iteratione sermonis vitanda</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e114"> ¶
      Rubrica. 9
      <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>sus filius sirach in ecclesiast.
      <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>c. 7. <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e120">Non interes sermo
        <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>nem in tua oratione.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e126"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e128"> c. 42. Non
        <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>duplices sermonem. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e134">
               <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e138">¶ Gaufridus in poetria. c. 41. Respuat au
        <lb ed="#V" n="20" break="no"/>diri bis idem. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e145">
               <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e149">¶ De multiplicatione verborum.
        <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>Alomon in prouerbiis
        <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>c. 10. In mul
        <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>tiloquio non deest peccatum. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e159">
               <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e163">¶ Aristotelis retho. li. 3. et fi. c 18
        <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>Oportet non prolixe narrare: sicut neque pro
        <lb ed="#V" n="27" break="no"/>hemizare prolixe: neque persuasiones dicere. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e171">
               <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e175">¶ Oratius in poetria: Quicquid precipies
        <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>esto breuis: vt cito dicta
        <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>Percipiant animi dociles teneantque fideles
        <lb ed="#V" n="31"/>Omne superuacuum pleno de pectore manat. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e185">
               <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e189">¶ Tullius retho. artis vereris: li. i. c. 10. Se
        <lb ed="#V" n="33"/>pe res parum est intellecta longitudine ma
        <lb ed="#V" n="34" break="no"/>gis quam obscuritate narrationis. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e197"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e199"> 11. c. Bre
        <lb ed="#V" n="35"/>uitas orationis est cum nisi necessarium nul
        <lb ed="#V" n="36" break="no"/>lum assumitur verbum. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e207"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e209"> 14. c. et fi. Commo
        <lb ed="#V" n="37"/>tis animis diutius in conquestione morari
        <lb ed="#V" n="38"/>non oportebit. Quemadmodum enim di
        <lb ed="#V" n="39" break="no"/>xit Appolius retho. Lachryma nihil citius
        <lb ed="#V" n="40"/>arescit. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e222"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e224"> Idem retho. artis noue: lib. i. c. 5.
        <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>Quo breuior eo lucidior et cognita facilior
        <lb ed="#V" n="42"/>narratio est. / Li. 2. c. 7. Conmiserationem
        <lb ed="#V" n="43"/>breuem esse oportet: nihil enim lachryma
        <lb ed="#V" n="44"/>citius arescit. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e236"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e238"> Idem de iure ciuili et iusti
        <lb ed="#V" n="45" break="no"/>tia naturali: siue de legibus. l. iii. Breuitas 
        <!--202.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>magna laus est in sententia: nec est vnquam lo
        <lb ed="#V" n="47"/>ga oratione vtendum.
        <lb ed="#V" n="48"/>Lex cod. ti. de veteri iure enucleando. li. ii.
        <lb ed="#V" n="49"/>Multo vtilius pauca indonee effundere quam
        <lb ed="#V" n="50"/>multis inutilibus homines pregrauari. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e259">
               <lb ed="#V" n="51"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e263">¶ Priscianus in prohemino: In magna ope
        <lb ed="#V" n="52"/>ris materia impossibile est aliquid perfe
        <lb ed="#V" n="53" break="no"/>ctum breuiter exponi. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e271"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e273"> Li. 7. ti. de vocati
        <lb ed="#V" n="54" break="no"/>uo singulari sede declinationis: Iuniores
        <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>breuitate gaudent. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e281">
               <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e285">¶ Gregorius in pastorali. c. 16. Sepe dicto
        <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>rum virtus perditur: cum apud corda audiem
        <lb ed="#V" n="58"/>tium loquicitas incauta opportunitateleuigatur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e293">
               <lb ed="#V" n="59"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e297">¶ Isydorus soliloquiorum: li. 2. c. 13. Tol
        <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>le verbositatem sermonis superflui. Mul
        <lb ed="#V" n="61" break="no"/>tiloquium non effugiet culpam. Breuem. ser
        <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>monem scientia facit. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e308">
               <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e312">¶ Mattheus vintoniensis in poetria partur.
        <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>i. c. 8. Prolixitas nouerca est memorie. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e318"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e320"> 9.
        <lb ed="#V" n="65"/>c. Breuitas sibi aperta sibi amicat audatiam.
        <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>10. c. Uerborum confusio nouerca est in
        <lb ed="#V" n="67" break="no"/>telligentie: et doctrine pretendit offendi cul
        <lb ed="#V" n="68" break="no"/>tum. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e332"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e334"> 22. c. Prolixitas fastidii puerpera
        <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>est. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e340"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e342"> Partur. 2. c. 3. Infinitas nouerca est di
        <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>scipline et amica confusionis. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e348">
               <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e352">¶ Iacobus beneuentanus. c. 5. 7. et pe. Inui
        <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>diam generat et longus tedia sermo. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-d1e358">
               <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d66288-Qd1e362">¶ Iudex venusinus: li. de ptractatione nuptur.
        <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>c. i. Sermo breuis longo gratior esse solet. </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
